{"tid":1821794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蔡英文回應香港的朋友","createTime":"2020-01-12T14:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T15:34:08.000Z","uid":34869,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"769c59e58e663c243d4fc1c2accdb1d93fbb3977","tid":1821794,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10156368927336065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fposts%2F10156368927336065&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=be348cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10156368927336065</a><br />\n<br />\n這次，台灣人民勇敢而自信的決定，讓世界看見台灣人民的聲音。<br />\n  <br />\n過去這半年來，有許多香港的年輕朋友，在台灣各個角落自發的舉著牌子和旗子，告訴台灣人民香港所發生的事情。<br />\n  <br />\n在網路上，台灣的年輕人也透過社群和香港同步感受民主自由的重要。<br />\n  <br />\n選前一天我說，全世界都會看到，台灣人守住了這座民主堡壘。<br />\n  <br />\n香港的朋友，你們看到了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLoQcM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLoQcM0.jpg&h=43790416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辣台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6357385148ff8a3037e1fd5abe556b428645b1","tid":1821794,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8393c1c7408ae8bdfb8a43ec26891fe6710a2ba","tid":1821794,"ui